OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA dry and largely fine Easter
OL,6,FMonday with plenty of sunshine.
OL,7,FFeeling a little warmer than the
OL,8,Fweekend, especially in the sunshine
OL,9,Fand lighter winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA dry and clear night to come
OL,12,Fwith perhaps a few mist and fog
OL,13,Fpatches forming. A chilly night with
OL,14,Fperhaps a frost in the countryside.
OL,15,
OL,16,CTuesday:FA sunny start to the day,
OL,17,Falthough high cloud will gradually
OL,18,Fmove in from the west making the
OL,19,Fsunshine hazy by lunchtime. Feeling
OL,20,Fwarm, especially in the sunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
